dc_title_s: Thirty Year Precipitation dataset (1971-2000) for the Susquehanna River Basin'
dc_description_s: 30 Year Precipitation dataset (1971-2000) for the Susquehanna River Basin (2006 boundary). This dataset was created from a precipitation raster from the Spatial Climate Analysis Service, Oregon State University. Please use the GRIDCODE field for precipitation in inches. The correct conversion appears in the Entity and Attribute; Overview Description section of this document.
